findStrings.find: A link return to Login screen must be always available in Register screen
Register screen must be displayed after user tapped on Register Link
User cannot register account with Full name contains only one word, an error message displayed to user: Họ và tên phải có ít nhất 02 từ
User cannot register account with Full name contains below 6 characters, an error message displayed to user: Họ và tên bắt buộc phải chứa ít nhất 6 kí tự.
After registered with a fake/unformatted phone numbers, system must display error message: "Please use your actual phone numbers" and focus to the field
After registered with an existed phone numbers, system must send error message to user: "The phone numbers are in used, please use a different phone numbers"
When typing less than 6 characters into Password field, error "Password must contain at least 6 characters" should appear
After registered with valid information, a message should be displayed to User: "Thank you for registering, Please check PIN code to verify in the next step"
